<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3472380>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Growth line traces of Turritellidae species based on own data; bold: type species of genera; black: Paratethyan species; asterisk: non-Paratethyan species (unknown basal sinuses are left blank)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3472380/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3472384>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. A–C. Turritella inaequicingulata Hölzl, 1958, Nondorf (Austria); A1–A2. NHMW 1912/0001/0013. B1–B2. NHMW 1912/0001/0012. C1–C2. NHMW 1860/0050/0268. D1–D2. Turritella terebralis Lamarck, 1822, Léognan (France), NHMW 1850/0018/0100). E–F. Turritella gradata Menke in Hörnes, 1855. E. lectotype, Weinsteig (Austria), NHMW 1846/0037/0397. F1–2. Stetten-Teiritzberg (Austria), NHMW 2018/0169/0001." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3472384/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3472370>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Paleogeography of the Paratethys during the early Miocene (Burdigalian, Eggenburgian, Sakaraulian) and the middle Miocene (Langhian, Badenian, Tarkhanian) (modified after Popov et al. 2004 and Neubauer et al. 2015)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3472370/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3472372>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Miocene chronostratigraphy after Gradstein et al. (2012) with regional Paratethys stages after Popov et al. (2004) and Piller et al. (2007)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3472372/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3472386>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. A. Turritella inaequicingulata Hölzl 1958, NHMW 2018/0165/0001, Mörtersdorf (Austria) with a specimen of Peyrotia desmarestina (de Basterot, 1825), indicated by an arrow. B. Turritella gradata Menke in Hörnes, 1855, Weinsteig (Austria), NHMW 2018/0165/0002." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3472386/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

